desc: WellBeSleep® - a product series of shots and bars for people who have trouble falling asleep at night, or wake up in the middle of the night and can’t go back to sleep. WellBeSleep Shot and Bar contain lemon balm that can make you falling asleep easier.

layout.text: Trouble winding down after a long day? Or just need that extra help to relax, close your eyes and fall asleep?
